{"type":"message","id":"288583bf","parentId":"c105ec1f","timestamp":"2026-02-27T22:43:42.973Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"الـ skill مش موجود بعد. أنا هأكتبه لك بس الملف مش ظاهر. دعني أشتغل في مسار صحيح:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call-ef685311-008b-41a8-99ac-f1cfaf9daaed","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/egx-news/SKILL.md","content":"# egx-news\n\n## Goal\nSearch for Egyptian stock market (EGX) news and send me a Telegram notification with a summary.\n\n## Skill Details\n- Name: egx-news\n- Description: Daily Egyptian stock market briefing with top news and EGX30 movement\n\n## What it should do\n1. Search the web for: \"\\u0628\\u0648\\u0631\\u0635\\u0629 \\u0645\\u0635\\u0631 \\u0627\\u0644\\u064a\\u0648\\u0645\" AND \"EGX30\" AND \"\\u0623\\u0633\\u0647\\u0645 \\u0645\\u0635\\u0631\"\n2. Extract the most important 5 news items\n3. Format a clean Arabic summary with:\n   - \\ud83d\\udcc8 \\u062d\\u0631\\u0643\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0633\\u0648\\u0642 (up/down/flat)\n   - \\ud83d\\udcf0 \\u0623\\u0647\\u0645 5 \\u0623\\u062e\\u0628\\u0627\\u0631 \\u0645\\u0639 \\u0645\\u0635\\u062f\\u0631\\u0647\\u0627\n   - \\u26a1 \\u0623\\u064a \\u0641\\u0631\\u0635 \\u0623\\u0648 \\u0645\\u062e\\u0627\\u0637\\u0631 \\u062a\\u0644\\u0641\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0627\\u0646\\u062a\\u0628\\u0627\\u0647\n4. Send the summary to me via Telegram\n\n## Schedule\nRun this skill automatically every day at:\n- 9:00 AM (\\u0641\\u062a\\u062d \\u0627\\u0644\\u0628\\u0648\\u0631\\u0635\\u0629)\n- 2:30 PM (\\u0625\\u063a\\u0644\\u0627\\u0642 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0628\\u0648\\u0631\\u0635\\u0629)\n\n## Output format (Arabic)\n\\ud83c\\udfe6 *\\u062a\\u0642\\u0631\\u064a\\u0631 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0628\\u0648\\u0631\\u0635\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0635\\u0631\\u064a\\u0629*\n\\ud83d\\udd50 [\\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0648\\u0642\\u064a\\u062a]\n\\ud83d\\udcc8 *\\u062d\\u0631\\u0643\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0633\\u0648\\u0642:* [\\u0645\\u0644\\u062e\\u0635]\n\\ud83d\\udcf0 *\\u0623\\u0647\\u0645 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u062e\\u0628\\u0627\\u0631:*\n1. [\\u062e\\u0628\\u0631] - [\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0635\\u062f\\u0631]\n2. [\\u062e\\u0628\\u0631] - [\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0635\\u062f\\u0631]\n...\n\\u26a1 *\\u0645\\u0644\\u0627\\u062d\\u0638\\u0627\\u062a:* [\\u0623\\u064a \\u0641\\u0631\\u0635 \\u0623\\u0648 \\u0645\\u062e\\u0627\\u0637\\u0631]\n\n## Important\n- Use web search to get REAL current news, not made up data\n- If market is closed, still send available news\n- Keep it concise, max 300 words"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"arcee-ai/trinity-large-preview:free","usage":{"input":17927,"output":1090,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19017,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772232185028}}
