{"type":"message","id":"c79d567c","parentId":"faefa67c","timestamp":"2026-02-27T22:54:36.897Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ممكن نعمله مجاني بطرق كتير:\n\n**الطريقة 1:** DuckDuckGo API (مجاني)\n```bash\ncurl \"https://api.duckduckgo.com/?q=Keroles+Monsef&format=json\"\n```\n\n**الطريقة 2:** Bing API (مجاني)\n```bash\ncurl \"https://api.bing.com/search?q=Keroles+Monsef\"\n```\n\n**الطريقة 3:** Google Custom Search (فيه حد أقصى مجاني)\n```bash\ncurl \"https://www.googleapis.com/customsearch/v1?q=Keroles+Monsef&key=YOUR_KEY\"\n```\n\n**الطريقة 4:** Use a free API service\n```bash\ncurl \"https://free-api.com/search?q=Keroles+Monsef\"\n```\n\n**الطريقة 5:** Use Python with free libraries\n```bash\npython3 -c \"import requests; print(requests.get('https://api.duckduckgo.com/?q=Keroles+Monsef&format=json').text)\"\n```\n\nدلوقتي جرب واحدة من دول:\n\n```bash\ncurl \"https://api.duckduckgo.com/?q=Keroles+Monsef&format=json\"\n```\n\nدول أول حاجة. أي واحدة جربها وأقولك النتيجة."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"arcee-ai/trinity-large-preview:free","usage":{"input":23451,"output":294,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23745,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772232863975}}
